2026-XX-YY v. 0.99.3
--------------------
- Improved AboutDialog content
- Used YPaned into OptionDialog and changed the minimum size to 640x300
- Fixed logging not starting when enabled but no directory was configured:
  home directory is now used as default and persisted in user preferences
- Fixed logging silently disabled when the configured log directory does not
  exist: a warning dialog is now shown at startup

2026-05-31 v. 0.99.2
--------------------
- Changed layout using tabs (requires python-manatools 0.99.2)
- ActiveBindings tree is on requested now as external dialog
- Added Service->Module management
- Added document-edit icon button -> fallback is "&Edit" string
- Added IP Set management, if enable into layout option settings
- Improved configuration loading (user settings)

2026-04-12 v. 0.99.1
--------------------
- Moved to manatools aui
- Added Automatic Helper Assignment Change management
- Added Log Denied Change management
- Added Default Zone Change management
- Added Lockdown enabling/disabling management
- Added Panic Mode enabling/disabling management
- New option dialog to manage settings, such as logging or firewall configuration
- Added option to make runtime configuration permanent
- Fixed Services and ICMP Filter management (using right columns)
- Added configuration file (manafirewall.yaml)
- Added logging (to be enabled by user settings/configuration file)

